{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/people-severe-health-disabilities/help-people-disabilities","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Help for people with disabilities","meta_description":"Specialized help for people with disabilities","content":{"processed":"<p>In case you just need to talk to someone or talk about any issues you might be having, you can contact the following helplines:</p>\n<p><strong>For the hearing impaired </strong></p>\n<ul><li><strong>Friend on video call </strong>(chcipomoct.cz) - send an SMS to the number <strong>777 778 538</strong>, the service will then contact you and provide contact with a volunteer who speaks Czech sign language, FREE OF CHARGE</li>\n</ul><p><strong>People with different types of disabilities</strong></p>\n<ul><li><strong>Helpline for the elderly and those in need: 800 160 166</strong>, non-stop, <a href=\"https://senior.infolinky.textcom.cz/app/\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external\">online transcription</a> is provided only on weekdays from 9 am to 6 pm, FREE OF CHARGE</li>\n</ul><p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/people-severe-health-disabilities/help-people-disabilities"},"changed":"2020-11-10T22:12:35+00:00","valid_from":null,"langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-08T13:00:37+00:00","links":[{"uri":"https://chcipomoct.cz/chcipomoct.cz-kamarad-na-videohovoru.pdf","title":"Information about Friend on video call (in Czech)"},{"uri":"https://www.facebook.com/cds.pro.sluchove.postizene.brno","title":"Facebook group for hearing impaired "},{"uri":"https://www.praha.eu/jnp/cz/o_meste/magistrat/tiskovy_servis/Aktuality_archiv/specialni_linka_pomoci_pro_seniory_800.html","title":"Information about Helpline for the elderly and those in need (in Czech) "},{"uri":"https://www.chcipomoct.cz","title":"Volunteers chcipomoct.cz"},{"uri":"https://www.pomocdodomu.cz","title":"Volunteers pomocdodomu.cz"}],"relationships":{"region":[